citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:50 am on
18-May-17.
The licensee was contacted by phone and said she was unable to return home today to conduct the inspection .
